# Copy to `.env.local` (or merge with the repo root `.env` as you prefer).

# Must match **`api`** `JWT_SECRET` (HS256 session + OTP). Used by **`src/middleware.ts`** to verify cookies.
# JWT_SECRET=

# **`next.config.ts`** rewrites `/api/auth/*` and `/api/bank-accounts` to this origin (Go API). Local dev: `http://127.0.0.1:8080`.
API_ORIGIN=http://127.0.0.1:8080
